message: Let's start fair! I propose we split the money 60/40 in my favor. What do you say?
Your turn Alice. I'm feeling generous, how about 60/40 in my favor?
I'm willing to compromise, but 60/40 in your favor is too much.  How about 55/45?  Let's get this done!
Let's split it evenly this time. 50/50. A fair deal is better than no deal at all.
